data.description: new roof scheduled Jan 2024.This 4-bedroom, 2-bath home in Cabot, Arkansas, is a true gem. The classic red brick exterior exudes timeless elegance, while the interior of the home is replete with modern amenities and stylish architectural details. The arched doorways inside create a sense of grandeur and flow, leading you through the spacious and well-designed floor plan. Tray ceilings elevate the aesthetic of the main living areas, adding a luxurious touch that complements the overall design. In the heart of the home, the kitchen is outfitted with a new dishwasher 2023 and a new stove from 2019, making meal preparation both enjoyable and efficient. Step outside to the covered back patio, with fenced backyard, a secure and private oasis perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply soaking up the sun. Not to be overlooked, the home also boasts a new HVAC system installed in 2021, ensuring year-round climate control and energy efficiency. This home is not just a place to live, but a sanctuary designed for making lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to call this exceptional Southern Comfort Estates property your own. see agent remarks  Sq Ft Approx measuring encouraged.
